    "In 2021, Xie et al. (2021) proposed a forward-secure lattice-based proxy signature scheme.",
    "As the name implies, the scheme has forward security, but the scheme needs to improve its security at the cost of efficiency.",
    "The overview Table 4 we provided for lattice-based digital signatures offers a visual comparison of different scheme properties.",
